gs to Do</a></li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"cp-navbar__mega-col\">\n              <h4><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/bulverde/\">Bulverde</a></h4>\n              <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/bulverde/neighborhoods/\">Neighborhoods</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.idxbroker.com/idx/search/advanced\">Home Search</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/bulverde/restaurants/\">Restaurants</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/bulverde/things-to-do/\">Things to Do</a></li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/blog\" class=\"cp-navbar__link\">Blog</a></li>\n        <li class=\"cp-navbar__dropdown\">\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"cp-navbar__link\">Resources</a>\n          <ul class=\"cp-navbar__sub\">\n            <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/about\">About Cody</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/properties\">Portfolio</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/testimonials\">Testimonials</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/buyers-guide\">Buyer's Guide</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/sellers-guide\">Seller's Guide</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/sellers-net-sheet\">Seller's Net Sheet</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/mortgage-calculator\">Mortgage Calculator</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/closing-costs\">Closing Cost Estimator</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/relocation-guide\">Relocation Guide</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/recommended-lenders\">Recommended Lenders</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/faq\">FAQ</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n        <li><a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/#contact\" class=\"cp-navbar__link\">Let's Connect</a></li>\n      </ul>\n    </nav>\n\n    <a href=\"tel:+18303605569\" class=\"cp-btn cp-btn-primary cp-navbar__cta\">\n      (830) 360-5569\n    </a>\n\n    <button class=\"cp-navbar__hamburger\" id=\"cpHamburger\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\">\n      <span></span><span></span><span></span>\n    </button>\n  </div>\n</header>\n\n<!-- ============ IDX CONTENT GOES HERE ============ -->\n<main class=\"cp-idx-main\">\n  <div class=\"cp-idx-container\">\n","footer":"  </div>\n</main>\n\n<!-- ============ SITE FOOTER ============ -->\n<footer class=\"cp-footer\">\n  <div class=\"cp-footer__bottom\">\n    <p class=\"cp-footer__disclaimer\">\n      Popby Realty | Office: (830) 321-0051 | 323 Arendes Dr, New Braunfels, TX 78130<br />\n      All information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed and should be independently reviewed and verified.<br />\n      <a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/docs/trec-consumer-protection-notice.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"cp-footer__legal-link\">TREC Consumer Protection Notice</a> | <a href=\"https://cposeyrealestate.com/docs/trec-iabs.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"cp-footer__legal-link\">TREC Information About Brokerage Services</a>\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"cp-footer__copy\">\n      &copy; <span id=\"cp-year\"></span> Cody Posey Real Estate. All rights reserved.\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</footer>\n\n<!-- Mobile contact bar -->\n<div class=\"cp-mobile-bar\">\n  <a href=\"tel:+18303605569\">📞 Call</a>\n  <a href=\"sms:+18303605569\">💬 Text</a>\n  <a href=\"mailto:codyposey@cposeyrealestate.com\">✉ Email</a>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  document.getElementById('cp-year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();\n  var hb = document.getElementById('cpHamburger');\n  var nm = document.getElementById('cpNavMenu');\n  if (hb && nm) hb.addEventListener('click', function() { nm.classList.toggle('open'); });\n  window.addEventListener('scroll', function() {\n    var nav = document.getElementById('cp-navbar');\n    if (!nav) return;\n    if (window.scrollY > 50) nav.classList.add('scrolled');\n    else nav.classList.remove('scrolled');\n  });\n\n  /* ============================================================\n     LEAD CAPTURE OVERRIDE\n     On listing detail pages, replace IDX's \"Contact Agent\" form\n     with a CTA button that sends the user to our own contact form\n     pre-filled with the listing address & MLS#.\n     ============================================================ */\n  function injectLeadCTA() {\n    if (!/\\/idx\\/details\\//i.test(window.location.pathname)) return;\n    if (document.querySelector('.cp-cta-button[data-cp-injected]')) return;\n\n    // Pull listing context from the page\n    var addressEl = document.querySelector(\n      '.IDX-detailsHeaderAddress, [itemprop=\"streetAddress\"], h1.IDX-detailsHeader, .IDX-resultsAddress'\n    );\n    var mlsEl = document.querySelector('.IDX-listingID, [itemprop=\"mlsNumber\"], .IDX-mlsNumber');\n    var address = addressEl ? addressEl.textContent.trim() : '';\n    var mls = mlsEl ? mlsEl.textContent.replace(/[^\\w-]/g, '').trim() : '';\n\n    var params = new URLSearchParams();\n    params.set('source', 'idx-detail');\n    if (address) params.set('listing', address);\n    if (mls) params.set('mls', mls);\n    params.set('url', window.location.href);\n    var contactUrl = 'https://cposeyrealestate.com/contact?' + params.toString();\n\n    // Build the CTA block\n    var wrap = document.createElement('div');\n    wrap.className = 'cp-cta-block';\n    wrap.style.cssText = 'margin:1.5rem 0;padding:1.5rem;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;border-radius:4px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.06);';\n    wrap.innerHTML =\n      '<h3 style=\"font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;font-size:1.1rem;margin:0 0 .5rem;color:#000;\">Interested In This Property?</h3>' +\n      '<p style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#555;margin:0 0 1rem;line-height:1.5;\">Get more details, schedule a private showing, or ask Cody anything about this listing.</p>' +\n      '<a href=\"' + contactUrl + '\" class=\"cp-cta-button\" data-cp-injected=\"1\">Request More Info / Schedule Showing</a>' +\n      '<a href=\"tel:+18303605569\" class=\"cp-cta-button cp-cta-button--secondary\">Call Cody: (830) 360-5569</a>';\n\n    // Place the CTA next to the listing photos / above the description.\n    // Try several anchor points in order of preference.\n    var anchor =\n      document.querySelector('#IDX-detailsContactWrapper') ||\n      document.querySelector('.IDX-detailsContact') ||\n      document.querySelector('.IDX-detailsSidebar') ||\n      document.querySelector('#IDX-detailsRightCol') ||\n      document.querySelector('.IDX-detailsHeader') ||\n      document.querySelector('#IDX-main');\n\n    if (!anchor) return;\n    if (anchor.parentNode && anchor.id === 'IDX-detailsContactWrapper') {\n      anchor.parentNode.insertBefore(wrap, anchor);\n    } else {\n      anchor.insertBefore(wrap, anchor.firstChild);\n    }\n  }\n\n  // IDX renders content async — observe and re-run until injected.\n  if (document.readyState === 'loading') {\n    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', injectLeadCTA);\n  } else {\n    injectLeadCTA();\n  }\n  var attempts = 0;\n  var poll = setInterval(function() {\n    attempts++;\n    injectLeadCTA();\n    if (document.querySelector('.cp-cta-button[data-cp-injected]') || attempts > 20) {\n      clearInterval(poll);\n    }\n  }, 500);\n</script>\n\n"}